Compile project:
    javac -d bin/ src/*.java

Run project:
    java --class-path "bin;lib/sqlite-jdbc.jar" Application


Package project:
    jar cf dist/Application.jar -C bin .

Run package:
    java -jar dist/Application.jar

For the application to work, the following steps are required:

1.) Create a directory named "lib";

2.) Download sqlite-jdbc.jar from here:
https://mvnrepository.com/artifact/org.xerial/sqlite-jdbc ;

3.) Add the downloaded sqlite-jdbc.jar to the "lib" directory;

* ) Don't forget to rename the downloaded file to "sqlite-jdbc.jar".



